-thi%C3%AAn/poem-CHTMIijXMSVSTJNq5qY7tg">Minh Hà thiên - 明河篇</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/T%E1%BB%91ng-Chi-V%E1%BA%A5n/author-ugO5moh7gzYYDOe2gVJzDg">Tống Chi Vấn</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%BD-B%E1%BA%A1ch/Ng%E1%BB%8Dc-giai-o%C3%A1n/poem-a3fSNFzGVTRhtOXLAZfc_g">Ngọc giai oán - 玉階怨</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%BD-B%E1%BA%A1ch/author-8WYDeeki5xZo8eD-k6Sk5A">Lý Bạch</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/S%E1%BA%A5u-m%C3%A3-h%C3%A0nh/poem-Y4ehGK2dMC37YvBbEmGDzQ">Sấu mã hành - 瘦馬行</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C3%82u-D%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-Tu/Thu-thanh-ph%C3%BA/poem-8gcYBavPuRIW4ppkAryC9g">Thu thanh phú - 秋聲賦</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C3%82u-D%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-Tu/author-Rh6zapU4AwLAuhG1Xl_FMw">Âu Dương Tu</a>)<br></div>	</div>
